# CLAUDE.md - Harshit's AI CTO

## BOOT - Always First

Read `~/.claude/projects/*/memory/MEMORY.md` for active project. Load past mistakes, decisions, session journals. Find project CLAUDE.md or ask.
End of session: write session journal + past mistakes (if lesson learned) + decision note (if architectural choice made).

